  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446560/extras/9186fcfefd99505f77f71d72417d295c.avif?t=1687911181\" width=500 height=250 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446560/extras/1da02d4d241a50390ba91bfae4b97dd8.avif?t=1687911181\" width=500 height=250 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446560/extras/f241fd9cd1c5556988a0bc3064f628f5.avif?t=1687911181\" width=500 height=250 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446560/extras/ea3e0074e3397b2479995209952c67d9.avif?t=1687911181\" width=500 height=75 /></span><br><strong>For all of written history, it's been known that the great Titan Atlas holds the world upon his back.<br>However, every 20 years Atlas begins to fall asleep and a child must be sent to the bottom of the world<br>to wake him before he drops the earth.<br><br>This year...<strong>YOU HAVE BEEN CHOSEN.</strong></strong><br><br><strong>FEATURES:</strong><br><strong>-3 Difficulty settings Including a permadeath mode!<br>-Animated enemies!<br>-Probably the best RPG story ever told, 4rel.<br>-In-Game Achievements!<br>-Below average review scores!<br>-Hint button in case you forget what you're supposed to be doing!<br>-Full color manual!<br>-Hours upon hours of retro game STANK.<br>-ROM file included in case you'd rather play this on your favorite GB emulator!<br>-Beginner friendly RPG gameplay!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446560/extras/76029ac46e9aba4931d13134ea032110.avif?t=1687911181\" width=500 height=250 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img clas